sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Contract as WayneLockGuardianRecovery
    participant FWSS as Filecoin Warm Storage
    participant Lit as Lit Protocol

    User->>Contract: getEntryUids owner
    Contract-->>Browser: google facebook ssh-key

    User->>Browser: Click Retrieve on google
    Browser->>Contract: getEntry owner google
    Contract-->>Browser: metadataJson createdAt exists
    Browser->>Browser: Parse metadataJson

    Browser->>FWSS: fetchVaultBlob pieceCid serviceURL
    FWSS-->>Browser: encryptedBlob bytes

    Browser->>Lit: litDecryptDek ciphertext hash ACC
    Note right of Lit: Lit checks on-chain isRecoveryApprovedForOwner
    alt Guardian threshold met
        Lit-->>Browser: DEK bytes 32 bytes
        Browser->>Browser: AES-GCM decrypt encryptedBlob with DEK
        Browser-->>User: plaintext password
    else Threshold NOT met
        Lit-->>Browser: Error ACC not satisfied
        Browser-->>User: Guardian approval needed
    end
